author: Emma Tucker, CNN
title: DOJ charges 13 alleged members of violent Chicago gang in federal indictment
description: The Department of Justice has charged 13 members of a Chicago street gang faction with racketeering conspiracy as part of a federal indictment related to dozens of murders, attempted murders and acts of violence spanning more than 20 years.

author: Travis Caldwell, Joe Sutton, Keith Allen and Kelly McCleary, CNN
title: What we know about what happened at the Wisconsin Christmas parade
description: The celebratory sounds of a Wisconsin Christmas parade were interrupted by terrified screams Sunday after a vehicle plowed into participants and spectators gathered for the event in Waukesha, a city about 20 miles west of downtown Milwaukee.
